---
title: Caribbean Style Chicken and Roasted Vegetable Stew with Coriander Rice and Yoghurt
description: This Caribbean Style Chicken and Roasted Vegetable Stew is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
